item.title: Compiler help 87 errors
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

In your compiler, add:
sign/*.java
after:
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_05\bin\javac.exe” *.java

so it looks like:
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_05\bin\javac.exe” .java sign/.java
